# Copy this file to mbsyncrc and adjust the values.
#
# This example assumes email_backup.py is the only user of mbsync and keeps the
# local Maildir inside this repository.

IMAPAccount remote
Host imap.example.com
User you@example.com
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -a you@example.com -s email-backup-imap -w"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore remote-store
Account remote

MaildirStore local-store
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ./data/maildir/
Inbox ./data/maildir/INBOX

Channel mail-backup
Far :remote-store:
Near :local-store:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync Pull
Expunge Near
CopyArrivalDate yes
